{"word":"G4221 - ποτήριον - potḗrion - pot-ay'-ree-on - Cup","slug":"G4221","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ποτήριον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>potḗrion"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>pot-ay'-ree-on"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Cup"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C0;&#x03BF;&#x03C4;&#x03B7;&#x0301;&#x03C1;&#x03B9;&#x03BF;&#x03BD; - pote&#x0304;rion</b> - <i>pot-ay'-ree-on</i><p/>Neuter of a derivative of the alternate of <a href=\"#/G4095\">G4095</a>; a <i>drinking vessel</i>; by extension the contents thereof, that is, a <i>cupful</i> (<i>draught</i>); figuratively a <i>lot</i> or <i>fate:</i> - cup."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2666\">G2666</a>, <a href=\"#/G4095\">G4095</a>, <a href=\"#/G4188\">G4188</a>, <a href=\"#/G4213\">G4213</a>, <a href=\"#/G4222\">G4222</a>, <a href=\"#/G4224\">G4224</a>"}]}